text: haey nowpel del puokke bankheunh kar chuonhdaur ryy kar lengosabbay puokke ban bambek knea tow rk vea daoy puokke baohbng chaol anak( mou ham meat) aoy now chhr( sautr kho t hpeah) temnakeng . chaur anak pol tha avei del now cheamuoy a l laoh ku brasaer cheang kar lengosabbay ning chomnuonh towtiet . haey a l laoh chea anakaphdal leaphosakkar da brasaer bamphot
